{ Of course we should grab the pawn. } 8. O-O Nxd2
{ Black is ready to castle next, and basically just be a pawn up. I don't believe in the compensation. }
9. Re1+ Ne7
{ The knight will probably have to go here after d4-d5 anyway, so this is a sensible way to block the check. }
10. Bxd2 Bxd2 11. Qxd2 d5
{ Black castles next. It confuses me that Stockfish only gives =+, as I basically see a clean pawn up. But I won't argue with it. }
