{ This old move saw some romantic games once upon a time, but in the modern era, it will only bring White grief. }
7... Nxe4 8. O-O Bxc3 9. d5
{ 9.bxc3  d5=+  Black is basically just a pawn up. } 9... Ne5
{ I think this is the easiest solution. } 10. bxc3 Nxc4 11. Re1
{ Now, do me a big favor and don't play  11...f5  and allow  12.Bg5  .  I did this in a painful loss when I was 1400. }
11... Nd6 12. Ng5 O-O
{ Nice and simple. Black loses back his extra piece but remains a healthy pawn up. }
13. Nxe4 Nxe4 14. Rxe4 d6 { Pawn up. } *

