9... O-O 10. Be3 Bg4 11. Bxc6 bxc6 12. Qa4
{ This enterprising queen sortie has been tried a few times, but it's unsurprising White cannot get away with it. After }
12... f6 { The position immediately starts to crumble. } 13. Qxc6 Nxc3 14. Qxc3
Bxf3 15. gxf3 fxe5
{ Black equalizes material and is much better thanks to White's loose position. }
