{ Now, tempting as it might be to invade the second rank, Black absolutely needs to get rid of White's queenside pawn mass right away. }
20... Rxc3
{ An important resource. The position is now symmetrical, and Black equalizes thanks to the fork on d4.   See Huschenbeth, N. vs. Kryvoruchko, Y. in theModel Games chapter. }
