10. Ne2
{ This move is possible with h2-h3 and h7-h5 included as well, and here it meets a similar response. }
10... b6
{ Black has the ambitious plan of developing the bishop to b7 available to him, and his position is very straightforward.   I think he still has to be pretty accurate in the same position with h2-h3 and h7-h5 included, knowing some important moves down the road, but that is because Bc1-g5 is a possibility, while here it will just get kicked by h7-h6. Black is fine with easy moves like Bc8-b7 and c6-c5 coming soon. }
