{ Of course Black should be ready to meet the most natural move, grabbing the bishop pair, but it is nothing to be scared of. The rook ends up quite well placed on e6. }
14... Rxe6 15. g4 { 15.Rfe1  Rd8  Transposes tothe mainline. } 15... hxg4 16.
hxg4 Nh4
