17. Ne2
{ Now, Nd4 coming next could be scary, as could Bg3. Black cannot take the e5-pawn, as the Nd4 resource will cost him material. He only has one move to maintain the balance, and it just needs to be memorized. }
17... f5 18. gxf5 Nxf5
{ Black is ready for g5 next, when the bishop will be booted back to the passive h2 square and be vulnerable to Ra8-h8. White has nothing special here. }
